# Task 1: U.S. County-Year Panel Dataset

Author: Yuxin Shen

This repository contains the code and output for Task 1 of the coding test. The goal of this task is to construct a U.S. county-year panel dataset with consistent county identifiers and the following variables:

- State name
- County name
- State FIPS code
- County FIPS code
- Unemployment rate
- Income
- Population
- Income per capita

## Data sources

### 1. BEA
Source: BEA CAINC1, County Personal Income Summary

Variables used:
- Personal income
- Population
- Per capita personal income

Coverage used in this project:
- 1969 to 2024

### 2. BLS
Source: BLS Local Area Unemployment Statistics (LAUS), county annual averages

Variable used:
- Unemployment rate

Coverage used in this project:
- 1990 to 2024

